    "tour-ae-s1-body": "This quick tour shows you all the extra practice tools hiding in the sidebar. Takes about 30 seconds - or hit <em>Skip</em> to dive straight in.",
    "tour-ae-s1-title": "Additional Exercises 🎛️",
    "tour-ae-s2-body": "Click this toggle to expand a whole library of extra practice tools. Each one targets a different skill - grammar, vocabulary, listening, and more.",
    "tour-ae-s2-title": "The Additional Exercises section",
    "tour-ae-s3-body": "Learn natural multi-word expressions and collocations. The AI generates fresh chunks every session so you always have new language to absorb.",
    "tour-ae-s3-title": "Word Chunks",
    "tour-ae-s4-body": "Three exercise modes - error correction, sentence builder, and fill in the blank - all powered by AI so no two sessions are the same.",
