    "ob-btn-skip": "Skip tour",
    "ob-s1-body": "You've just created your account. This quick tour shows you where everything is and how to get the most out of your learning experience.",
    "ob-s1-title": "Welcome to Poly-Puff! 🎉",
    "ob-s2-body": "Before you start practising, take 2 minutes to complete your profile. Add your native language, English level, profession, and learning goals. The AI uses this information to <strong style=\"color:#56f0c0\">personalise every single exercise</strong> for you - making practice much more effective and relevant.",
    "ob-s2-cta": "→ Go to Profile",
    "ob-s2-skip": "I'll do it later",
    "ob-s2-title": "First: Complete Your Profile 👤",
    "ob-s3-body": "This page is your hub for everything. Every practice module is one click away - from Translation Trainer and Grammar to Vocabulary, Listening, Writing, and more. Bookmark this page so you can always find your way back.",
    "ob-s3-title": "Your Learning Hub 🏠",
    "ob-s4-body": "Translation Trainer is the flagship module. The AI gives you a sentence in your native language, you translate it into English, and you receive <strong style=\"color:#7ee8fa\">detailed grammar and vocabulary feedback</strong>. It works for every level, from A1 to C2.",
    "ob-s4-title": "Start Here: Translation Trainer ↔",
    "ob-s5-body": "Explore the full suite: <strong>Grammar Practice</strong>, <strong>Word Chunks</strong>, <strong>Vocabulary</strong> flashcards, <strong>Listening</strong>, and <strong>Writing</strong>. Each module uses AI-powered feedback tailored to your profile and level.",
    "ob-s5-title": "Practice Modules 📚",
    "ob-s6-body": "Track your scores, streaks, and improvement in <strong>Progress</strong>. Try the <strong>Daily Challenge</strong> to keep a streak going - consistent daily practice is the fastest route to fluency. We also have dedicated prep for <strong>IELTS</strong>, <strong>TOEFL</strong>, and <strong>Cambridge CAE</strong>.",
    "ob-s6-title": "Progress & Daily Challenge 📊",
    "ob-s7-body": "Start by completing your profile - then jump into Translation Trainer. The more you practise, the more personalised your experience becomes. Good luck!",
    "ob-s7-practice": "Start Practising",
    "ob-s7-profile": "Complete Profile",
    "ob-s7-title": "You're all set! 🚀",
