    "meetings-desc": "Lead and participate in professional meetings",
    "module-desc-business-english": "Business English focuses on workplace communication. It helps users practise emails, meetings, presentations, and professional language they can use with confidence.",
    "module-desc-cae-prep": "CAE C1 Advanced supports high-level English practice. It helps advanced learners refine precision, structure, and range so their English feels more polished and flexible.",
    "module-desc-classroom": "Share with Teacher lets students share Poly-Puff progress with their teacher through teacher groups and join codes, so support stays focused and accountable.",
    "module-desc-daily-challenge": "Daily Challenge keeps learning consistent. Short daily tasks help users build momentum, keep a streak, and make English practice feel manageable even on busy days.",
    "module-desc-generic": "{module} ले सिक्नेहरूलाई अंग्रेजी अभ्यास गर्ने केन्द्रित तरिका दिन्छ। यसले अभ्यास किन महत्त्वपूर्ण छ र कसरी राम्रो बानी, स्पष्ट वाक्य र बढी आत्मविश्वास बनाउँछ भनेर देखाउँछ।",
    "module-desc-grammar-practice": "Grammar Practice turns rules into usable habits. Instead of studying grammar in isolation, users correct, build, and test sentences so the rules become easier to apply while speaking and writing.",
    "module-desc-grammar-quiz": "Grammar Quiz gives quick, focused checks on grammar knowledge. It is useful for spotting weak areas, reinforcing corrections, and keeping practice active without needing a long study session.",
    "module-desc-ielts-prep": "IELTS Preparation trains the academic English skills needed for exam tasks. It supports structured writing, accuracy, vocabulary, and practice habits for test confidence.",
    "module-desc-listening": "Listening practice strengthens the bridge between written English and spoken English. It helps users recognise rhythm, pronunciation, and meaning in real time, which makes conversations feel less overwhelming.",
    "module-desc-placement-test": "Placement Test helps users understand their current English level. It gives a clearer starting point, so learners can practise at the right difficulty and see progress more meaningfully.",
    "module-desc-progress": "Progress helps users understand what is improving and what still needs attention. Seeing scores, streaks, and weaker areas makes learning feel visible and easier to plan.",
    "module-desc-toefl-prep": "TOEFL iBT Prep helps learners practise academic English for TOEFL-style tasks. It focuses on accuracy, comprehension, and clear responses under exam-like expectations.",
    "module-desc-translation-trainer": "Translation Trainer is the core exercise because it trains learners to move meaning from their native language into natural English. By translating full ideas instead of memorising isolated words, users practise thinking in English, noticing grammar patterns, and building sentences they can actually use in real conversations.",
    "module-desc-vocabulary-flashcards": "Vocabulary Flashcards help learners remember important words through repetition. The goal is not just recognition, but faster recall when users need the right word in writing, speaking, or translation.",
    "module-desc-vocabulary-vault": "Vocabulary Vault is a personal word bank. Users can save new words, review them later, and turn unfamiliar vocabulary into a focused practice list.",
    "module-desc-word-chunks": "Word Chunks helps learners stop building English one word at a time. It focuses on useful phrases, collocations, and natural building blocks so sentences sound smoother, faster, and more native-like.",
    "module-desc-writing": "Writing gives learners space to organise their thoughts in English. It builds accuracy, confidence, and fluency by helping users turn ideas into clear sentences and receive feedback on how to improve them.",
    "module-overview": "मोड्युल अवलोकन",
    "modules": "मोड्युलहरू",
    "my-day": "My Day",
