    "my-progress": "Ilọsiwaju mi",
    "name-poly": "lati Giriki polys: ọpọlọpọ, pupọ, tabi ju ọkan lọ.",
    "name-puff": "ẹmi rirọ tabi awọsanma kekere, ami si kikọ online ninu cloud.",
    "name-sub": "Poly wa lati ọrọ Giriki polys, itumọ rẹ ni ọpọlọpọ. Puff ranti awọsanma kekere rirọ, bii cloud intanẹẹti fun idaraya ede. Papọ, Poly-Puff tumọ si ọpọlọpọ ede ati ero ni ibi kikọ ti o rọ.",
