    "help-feedback-feature-text": "Thumela impendulo ngezindlela ezimbili: vula Impendulo kusuka kumenyu yomdwebo nganoma yisiphi isikhathi, noma uphendule i-pop-up evela ngokuzenzakalela ngemva kwemizabalazele eminingi. Izindlela zombili zikuvumela ukuthi ukhethe Impendulo, Iphutha noma Umbono futhi ufake i-imeyili yakho ukuze uthole impendulo.",
